{"ts":"2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z","author":"codex-root","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"## User story\n\nAs a coding or planning agent, I want one bounded and explainable relationship query for an item so that I can understand its purpose, execution order, downstream impact, and supporting evidence without guessing or loading unrelated history.\n\n## Token contract\n\nReturn the smallest useful summary first: item identity, state, immediate typed edges, critical path or blockers, evidence pointers, omitted counts, and a continuation token. Expand only on explicit demand or relevance thresholds.\n\n## Explainability contract\n\nEvery included node and edge carries a concise selection reason, source, age or freshness, and whether it is authoritative, inferred, approximate, or user-authored."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-8xr8"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"As an agent, I can traverse why an item exists, what it affects, what blocks it, and its evidence chain from one bounded graph query"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Provide one explainable, token-budgeted graph read that answers origin, prerequisites, dependents, impact, and evidence without separate full-tracker scans."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Story"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:graph","context-management","relationships","story","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":90},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"One request returns bounded ancestors, prerequisites, dependents, provenance, linked evidence, and the reason each node or edge was selected; Callers control direction, kind families, depth, node and edge limits, history window, token budget, fields, and cursor continuation; Default output is compact and counts-first; expanded and JSON or JSONL modes remain composable with grep, jq, and scripts; The response distinguishes complete, truncated, sampled, approximate, stale-index, and permission-redacted results; Public SDK, thin CLI, MCP action, and shell pipelines share one contract and deterministic ordering; Tests cover disconnected items, cycles in associative edges, missing endpoints, deep paths, concurrent mutations, and million-item bounded behavior"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/goal","value":"project management = context management"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/objective","value":"Make relationship context directly usable by coding agents through one predictable SDK and CLI flow"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/value","value":"Agents spend fewer tokens and tool calls reconstructing lineage and can justify every surfaced relationship"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/impact","value":"Reduces missed prerequisites, stale assumptions, duplicated work, and unbounded context dumps"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/outcome","value":"A bounded graph-context response with paths, semantic edge labels, evidence, truncation metadata, and continuation"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/why_now","value":"Current context comes from several list, get, deps, comments, history, and search calls while the dependency graph is under-specified"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-96h7"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/blocked_by","value":"pm-4jqm"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-4jqm","kind":"blocked_by","created_at":"2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z","author":"codex-root"},{"id":"pm-4k6b","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z"},{"id":"pm-96h7","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z"},{"id":"pm-bwyw","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-13T21:57:48.869Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Duplicate check 2026-07-13: all-status review found context packing and deps visualization items but no single agent story joining bounded lineage,impact,blockers,and evidence traversal; it belongs under pm-96h7."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"47d9ce976053693ff666984d026fbb489e21fb767fd054d4d9b4d06ae11cdd17","message":"Create bounded agent relationship context story"}
